sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 병원사업자(BIZ/HOSPITAL)
    participant JSP as detail.jsp
    participant C as CommunityPostController
    participant CS as CommunityCommentServiceImpl
    participant PM as CommunityPostMapper
    participant CM as CommunityCommentMapper
    participant PS as CommunityPostServiceImpl
    participant DB as Oracle

    User->>JSP: 답변 입력 후 등록
    JSP->>C: POST /community/comment
    C->>C: HttpSession memberInfo 확인
    C->>CS: insertComment(postId, body, member, parentId)
    CS->>CS: lookupMemberNo(member)
    CS->>PM: selectPostDetail(postId)
    PM->>DB: SELECT TB_POST
    DB-->>PM: BOARD_TYPE=LIFE
    CS->>CS: validateLifeCommentPermission
    CS->>CM: insertComment(vo)
    CM->>DB: INSERT TB_POST_COMMENT
    C->>PS: markLifeAnswered(postId)
    PS->>PM: updatePostTags ANSWERED
    PM->>DB: UPDATE TB_POST.TAGS
    C-->>JSP: redirect detail
